Angok Middle School, Kwak Mu Cheol.

33
00:02:37,986 --> 00:02:40,136
You killed her, didn't you?

34
00:02:41,216 --> 00:02:43,056
You killed my sister.

35
00:02:44,746 --> 00:02:47,256
What are you so afraid of?

36
00:02:48,226 --> 00:02:50,206
What about it?

37
00:02:50,206 --> 00:02:53,826
What do you want to hide so badly that you killed someone?

38
00:02:53,826 --> 00:02:55,996
In this place,

39
00:02:56,916 --> 00:02:59,146
you killed my sister...

40
00:02:59,146 --> 00:03:00,960
Dae Beom.

41
00:03:01,656 --> 00:03:03,340
What are you talking about?

42
00:03:04,186 --> 00:03:05,386
That's not true.

43
00:03:05,386 --> 00:03:07,896
