54
00:03:54,766 --> 00:03:56,456
Then what about this?

55
00:03:56,456 --> 00:03:59,266
Do you know what this graffiti means?

56
00:03:59,266 --> 00:04:02,706
You would know better about what Geun Ho saw before.

57
00:04:02,706 --> 00:04:04,566
How dare you speak like that?

58
00:04:04,566 --> 00:04:07,086
It's all over for you guys.

59
00:04:07,086 --> 00:04:10,556
It's just graffiti to us, but do you think the specialist won't know?

60
00:04:10,556 --> 00:04:13,466
How dare you threaten me with that stupid graffiti?

61
00:04:13,466 --> 00:04:16,046
How will you explain the surveillance footage?

62
00:04:16,046 --> 00:04:19,296
I bet he thought he wasn't visible if he called Geun Ho from the staircase.

63
00:04:19,296 --> 00:04:23,106
Who would expect to see his reflection in Geun Ho's window?

64
00:04:23,106 --> 00:04:26,356
Geun Ho, come here.

65
00:04:30,456 --> 00:04:32,286
Come here!

66
00:04:43,866 --> 00:04:45,286
Right?

67
00:04:45,286 --> 00:04:48,896
You killed Grandma as well to cover up the murder of Seon Ah!

68
00:04:48,896 --> 00:04:50,986
Stop saying gibberish!

69
00:04:50,986 --> 00:04:52,936
What do you know?

70
00:04:55,216 --> 00:04:57,606
Now everyone will know about this.

71
00:04:57,606 --> 00:05:00,656
All will know that your son is a murderer!

72
00:05:02,836 --> 00:05:04,596
That's not true.

73
00:05:06,276 --> 00:05:09,426
I think you've got something wrong.

74
00:05:14,786 --> 00:05:20,086
Bom's grandmother wasn't killed by my son.

75
00:05:20,086 --> 00:05:22,336
I did it.

76
00:05:24,336 --> 00:05:28,396
Of course, I didn't mean to kill her.

77
00:05:30,356 --> 00:05:32,466
You should have been there then.

78
00:05:32,466 --> 00:05:35,146
You should have been there instead of her!

79
00:05:57,326 --> 00:05:59,946
