- Where should I take you?

81
00:06:07,226 --> 00:06:09,036
To Myeong Joo Police Station, please.

82
00:06:09,036 --> 00:06:10,896
Hey, stop there!

83
00:06:10,896 --> 00:06:13,846
- Hurry, please. Hurry!
- Hey, stop there.

84
00:06:19,666 --> 00:06:21,906
I'm on my way now.

85
00:06:21,906 --> 00:06:25,266
I have evidence for the homicide case.

86
00:06:25,266 --> 00:06:27,906
[Police]

87
00:06:37,576 --> 00:06:39,316
