- No, please.

91
00:06:47,406 --> 00:06:49,666
- Please keep driving.
- Stop the car!

92
00:06:49,666 --> 00:06:51,946
- I said stop the car!
- Please trust me, just once.

93
00:06:51,946 --> 00:06:54,086
You know I'm on my way to the police station right now. So, please.

94
00:06:54,086 --> 00:06:55,986
Stop the car.

95
00:06:57,186 --> 00:06:59,896
Oh, no! Ahjussi!

96
00:07:11,826 --> 00:07:14,166
Ahjussi, please.

97
00:07:17,646 --> 00:07:20,856
Get out of the car. Get out now!

98
00:07:20,856 --> 00:07:22,726
