- Please trust me, just once, Ahjussi.

99
00:07:22,726 --> 00:07:24,926
Get out!

100
00:07:24,926 --> 00:07:27,856
Open the door. Open the door now!

101
00:07:27,856 --> 00:07:29,716
Open it!

102
00:07:35,446 --> 00:07:38,706
How dare he speak rudely like that to a citizen who pays taxes?

103
00:07:38,706 --> 00:07:41,926
Young Lady, hold on tight, okay?

104
00:07:41,926 --> 00:07:43,926
Thank you so much.

105
00:07:44,956 --> 00:07:48,166
It's not me! It's not me!

106
00:07:53,266 --> 00:07:54,856
[Police]

107
00:07:54,856 --> 00:07:56,416
[Homicide Squad]

108
00:08:15,336 --> 00:08:21,510
Geun Ho recalled the past by watching the video Dae Beom recorded.

109
00:08:22,306 --> 00:08:24,586
Seon Ah! Run away! It hurts!

110
00:08:24,586 --> 00:08:26,486
Geun Ho.

