120
00:09:08,306 --> 00:09:10,816
You got deceived by this woman!

121
00:09:10,816 --> 00:09:13,256
Those two are framing us!

122
00:09:13,256 --> 00:09:16,836
You wait and see. I won't sit back.

123
00:09:16,836 --> 00:09:18,796
We get it so go in there!

124
00:09:18,796 --> 00:09:21,616
Who killed the grandmother?

125
00:09:26,556 --> 00:09:29,316
Who killed Seon Ah?

126
00:09:32,806 --> 00:09:35,206
As we thought,

127
00:09:35,206 --> 00:09:40,256
Mr. Kwak and Mu Cheol were the culprits of this incident.

128
00:09:41,966 --> 00:09:46,126
