136
00:10:17,096 --> 00:10:21,756
I also don't know how such a story came out.

137
00:10:21,756 --> 00:10:25,936
Why did you just get punched?

138
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:33,396
I don't know. I think I wasn't in a sane mind, either.

139
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:41,276
But I wonder why Geun Ho wrote only the bottom of the name.

140
00:10:41,276 --> 00:10:45,196
If he'd written the whole name properly, the culprit would be caught long ago.

