153
00:12:00,186 --> 00:12:02,866
You rude little child!

154
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:07,726
Put on a show when you are on the air.

155
00:12:07,726 --> 00:12:11,126
Since you're a bit smart, you call me an idiot?

156
00:12:11,126 --> 00:12:13,110
Stand up. Hey!

157
00:12:50,270 --> 00:12:53,900
