161
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:53,046
Will you stay here while I'm gone?

162
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:57,166
I don't think it'll take that long.

163
00:14:00,740 --> 00:14:03,616
Okay, I'll do so.

