192
00:15:40,156 --> 00:15:42,086
Oh, that's good news.

193
00:15:42,086 --> 00:15:43,620
Yes, it is.

194
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:49,170
I know you must be sick of this town

195
00:15:49,170 --> 00:15:51,920
and want to leave soon,

196
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:55,120
but I'm a bit sad to see you go.

